      "# [2019/08/29-11:59:43][vortex.tools.storage][_ftpretrieve:0690][INFO]: ftpget on ftp://hendrix.meteo.fr//home/m/mxpt/mxpt001/vortex/arpege/pearp/DBLE/2017/06/01/T1800P/mb002/forecast/grid.arpege-forecast.euroc25+0003:00.grib (to: GRIB_EUROC25_0002+0003:00)\n",
      "# [2019/08/29-11:59:43][vortex.tools.net][get:0268][INFO]: FTP <get:/home/m/mxpt/mxpt001/vortex/arpege/pearp/DBLE/2017/06/01/T1800P/mb002/forecast/grid.arpege-forecast.euroc25+0003:00.grib>\n"
